-- Bheenick Says Mauritius to Cut Europe Dependency, Week-End Says
-- B y   K a m l e s h   B h u c k o r y
-- 2012-04-29T09:04:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-29/bheenick-says-mauritius-to-cut-europe-dependency-week-end-says.html
Mauritius should reduce its
dependency on  Europe , its main market, as the debt crisis
spreads, Week-End reported, citing Bank of Mauritius Governor
Rundheersing Bheenick.  The country needs to rapidly diversify its export markets,
the newspaper cited Bheenick as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Kamlesh Bhuckory in Port Louis at 
